Package task_3.view

Class View

  • java.lang.Object
    • task_3.view.View
  • public class View
extends java.lang.Object
    This class View represents the View layer from MVC model pattern. Class defines text constants used for messages preparation and the methods definition, used for showing the messages.
    Author:
    Igor Malianov https://github.com/malianov/MyHomework/tree/master/src/task_3
